<ul><li><a href="/wiki/Jang_Dong-gun" title="Jang Dong-gun">Jang Dong-gun</a> as Park Jae-hyuk<sup id="cite_ref-12" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-12">&#91;12&#93;</a></sup><sup id="cite_ref-13" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-13">&#91;13&#93;</a></sup>: An agent working for the South Korean <a href="/wiki/National_Intelligence_Service_(South_Korea)" title="National Intelligence Service (South Korea)">National Intelligence Service(NIS).</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Kim_Myung-min" title="Kim Myung-min">Kim Myung-min</a> as Chae Yi-do: A Police Detective Chief Inspector who leads a serial murder case and who fights hard to bring a criminal to justice.</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Lee_Jong-suk" title="Lee Jong-suk">Lee Jong-suk</a> as Kim Kwang-il<sup id="cite_ref-14" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-14">&#91;14&#93;</a></sup><sup id="cite_ref-auto_11-1" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-auto-11">&#91;11&#93;</a></sup><sup id="cite_ref-15" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-15">&#91;15&#93;</a></sup><sup id="cite_ref-16" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-16">&#91;16&#93;</a></sup><sup id="cite_ref-17" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-17">&#91;17&#93;</a></sup>: A key North Korean political figure's son who receives VIP treatment after his defection to South Korea, organised by the United States <a href="/wiki/Central_Intelligence_Agency" title="Central Intelligence Agency">Central Intelligence Agency (CIA)</a>. He becomes a prime suspect for a <a href="/wiki/Serial_killer" title="Serial killer">serial murder</a> case.</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Park_Hee-soon" title="Park Hee-soon">Park Hee-soon</a> as Ri Dae-bum: A North Korean police officer who secretly crosses the border into the South to track down Kim Kwang-il.</li></ul>
